<item>
            <title>[LU-7651] runtests test_1 fails with &#8216;old and new files are different: rc=22&apos;</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7651</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;runtests test_1 fails with &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;runtests test_1: @@@@@@ FAIL: old and new files are different: rc=22
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;From the client test_log, we see that many files differ:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;23:10:22:disable quota as required
23:10:34:comparing 772 previously copied files
23:10:45:Files /bin/mountpoint and /mnt/lustre/d1.runtests//bin/mountpoint differ
23:10:45:Files /bin/env and /mnt/lustre/d1.runtests//bin/env differ
23:10:45:Files /bin/ln and /mnt/lustre/d1.runtests//bin/ln differ
&amp;lt;- 70 lines of differing files removed -&amp;gt;
23:10:45:Files /bin/ipcalc and /mnt/lustre/d1.runtests//bin/ipcalc differ
23:10:45:Files /bin/basename and /mnt/lustre/d1.runtests//bin/basename differ
23:10:45:Files /bin/arch and /mnt/lustre/d1.runtests//bin/arch differ
23:10:45:Files /bin/sed and /mnt/lustre/d1.runtests//bin/sed differ
23:10:45:Files /bin/grep and /mnt/lustre/d1.runtests//bin/grep differ
23:10:45: runtests test_1: @@@@@@ FAIL: old and new files are different: rc=22 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There are no obvious errors in the console logs. &lt;/p&gt;

